extracted_metadata.title: Webinar: Exposing the Israeli Arms Industry
extracted_metadata.place: Azerbaijan to Myanmar or the Mexico
extracted_metadata.description: In this webinar, Green Olive is joined by an expert in the Israeli arms trade who researches for the Database of Israeli Military and Security Export (https://www.dimse.info/). Together we explore the diverse parts of the globe where Israeli weapons can be found, from Azerbaijan to Myanmar or the Mexico-US border.
